 of triumphing over adversity, and if your adversity is being an ambitious =
investment banker who also DJs then that is fine but I am going to make fun=
 of it.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In recent months, though, I have begun to thin=
k that I was wrong, and that the anonymous conservative older bankers who d=
oubted Solomon might (1) exist and (2) have been right that in fact no one =
man can successfully be both the CEO of Goldman Sachs and also a DJ. In Feb=
ruary <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31780057.258=
